Victor Osimhen has been presented with the Globe Soccer Emerging Player of the Year award. The Nigeria international was not able to attend the Globe Soccer Awards gala in Dubai on November 17, 2022. The award was presented to him in Naples on Wednesday.  The 24-year-old beat Barcelona star, Gavi and Real Madrid midfielder, Federico Valverde to the award. Osimhen has scored 10 goals in 13 league appearances for Napoli this season. He has been linked with a number of top clubs in Europe.